page_summary: This page outlines annotated Case Report Form (CRF) fields and SDTM/CDASH variables relevant to the collection and recording of tumor measurement data, lesion identification, evaluation methods, and response criteria such as RECIST 1.1 in breast cancer studies. It describes how to document tumor state, diameter, new lesion identification, and reasons for unevaluable tumors but does not define specific efficacy endpoints.
